        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " — theme: Built on Yesterday."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The Convention let five Founding Fathers debate a single topic in one round of monologues. The Founders' Court runs two rounds: opening statements where each founder reasons live with extended thinking, then a rebuttal round where each founder reads all four opponents' arguments and writes a targeted response naming them by name. Hamilton doesn't just state his view — he reads Jefferson's argument, picks the part he most disagrees with, and attacks it directly."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Worth noting alongside this: "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "link",
              "attrs": {
                "href": "https://advisoryhour.substack.com",
                "target": "_blank",
                "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow",
                "class": null
              }
            }
          ],
          "text": "Other week-4 entries"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " added more topics or polish; Founders' Court added a second debate round that makes the founders actually argue with each other instead of past each other"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null,
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "How the AI works"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bullet_list",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "Parallel extended thinking streams"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " — all five founders stream simultaneously via SSE. Each column shows a collapsible Reasoning panel with live thinking tokens, so you watch Washington deliberate before he speaks."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "Round 2 rebuttal mechanic"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " — after all five complete their opening statements, the frontend collects all five texts and fires a second round of parallel streams. Each founder receives the other four arguments, uses extended thinking to identify the strongest opposing claim, then writes a targeted 1-2 paragraph rebuttal naming the opponent directly. \"Hamilton's assertion that commerce requires...\" — that kind of specific."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "ElevenLabs voice synthesis"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " — each founder has a unique ElevenLabs voice ID. After their argument completes, click Speak to hear their verdict in their voice."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "textAlign": null,
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "How to play"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bullet_list",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Pick one of six modern constitutional controversies — AI rights, digital surveillance, executive power, and more."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Watch all five founders stream their opening arguments simultaneously. Click any Reasoning panel to expand the extended thinking."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "After round 1 completes, round 2 fires automatically. Watch each founder read the opposition and choose who to attack — the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "REBUTTAL"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " section appears below each opening statement."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list_item",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": null
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Click Speak on any founder after round 1 to hear their argument read aloud. The final verdict tallies all five votes."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
